"{\"uid\": \"twincities.com-2024-08-03-st-paul-sprinter-emmanuel-matadi-advances-into-100-meter-semifinals-for-first-time-in-three-olympic-trips\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Today's Paper  Sign up for Newsletters and Alerts  to submit an obituary  To place an obituary, please include the information from the obituary checklist below in an email toobits@pioneerpress.com.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 198, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is no option to place them through our website at this time.\", \"from\": 199, \"to\": 265, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Feel free to contact our obituary desk at 651-228-5263 with any questions.\", \"from\": 266, \"to\": 340, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"General Information:  Obituary Specification:  Policies:  Verification of Death:  In order to publish obituaries a name and phone number of funeral home/cremation society is required.\", \"from\": 342, \"to\": 525, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We must contact the funeral home/cremation society handling the arrangements during their business hours to verify the death.\", \"from\": 526, \"to\": 651, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If the body of the deceased has been donated to the University of Minnesota Anatomy Bequest Program, or a similar program, their phone number is required for verification.\", \"from\": 652, \"to\": 823, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please allow enough time to contact them especially during their limited weekend hours.\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 912, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A death certificate is also acceptable for this purpose but only one of these two options are necessary.\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 1018, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Guestbook and Outside Websites:  We are not allowed to reference other media sources with a guestbook or an obituary placed elsewhere when placing an obituary in print and online.\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1199, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We may place a website for a funeral home or a family email for contact instead; contact us with any questions regarding this matter.\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1333, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Obituary Process:  Once your submission is completed, we will fax or email a proof for review prior to publication in the newspaper.\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1467, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This proof includes price and days the notice is scheduled to appear.\", \"from\": 1468, \"to\": 1537, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please review the proof carefully.We must be notified of errors or changes before the notice appears in the Pioneer Press based on each day's deadlines.\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1691, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1647, \"end\": 1654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pioneer_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.9999311424214404, \"rank\": 6.2071720528625e-05, \"text\": \"Pioneer\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pioneer_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pioneer_Corporation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After publication, we will not be responsible for errors that may occur after final proofing.\", \"from\": 1693, \"to\": 1786, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Online:  Changes to an online obituary can be handled through the obituary desk.\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 1868, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Call us with further questions.\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1900, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Payment Procedure:  Pre-payment is required for all obituary notices prior to publication by the deadline specified below in our deadline schedule.\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 2049, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please call651-228-5263with your payment information after you have received the proof and approved its contents.\", \"from\": 2050, \"to\": 2163, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Credit Card:Payment accepted by phone only due to PCI (Payment Card Industry) regulations  EFT:Check by phone.\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2275, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please provide your routing number and account number.\", \"from\": 2276, \"to\": 2330, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rates:  Deadlines:  Please follow deadline times to ensure your obituary is published on the day requested.\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2441, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hours  Deadline (no exceptions)  Ad  Photos  MONDAY - FRIDAY  9:00AM - 5:00 PM  Next Day Publication  Must receive obituary content and payment same day by4:30PM  Make changes by5:00PM  Must receive photo(s) by 4:30PM  SATURDAYS  10:00AM - 2:00PM  Sunday Publication  Must receive obituary content and payment same day by1:30PM  Make changes by2:00PM  Must receive photo(s) by 1:30PM  SUNDAYS CLOSED          MEMORIAM (NON-OBITUARY) REQUEST  Unlike an obituary, Memoriam submissions are remembrances of a loved one who has passed.\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2973, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The rates for a memoriam differ from obituaries.\", \"from\": 2974, \"to\": 3022, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please call or email us for more memoriam information  Please call 651-228-5280 for more information.\", \"from\": 3024, \"to\": 3125, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"HOURS: Monday - Friday 8:00AM - 5:00PM (CLOSED WEEKENDS and HOLIDAYS)  Please submit your memoriam ad tomemoriams@pioneerpress.comor call 651-228-5280.\", \"from\": 3127, \"to\": 3278, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sign up for Newsletters and Alerts  Today's Paper  OUR PICKS:  Copyright \\u00a9 2025 MediaNews Group\", \"from\": 3282, \"to\": 3377, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3362, \"end\": 3377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Digital_First_Media\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"MediaNews Group\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Digital_First_Media\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Digital_First_Media\"}]}]}"